title: Combined Joint Task Force - Operation Inherent Resolve Spokesman to Brief (US Department of Defense) ...
text: ( Source : US Department of Defense ) Army Col. Steven Warren , spokesman, Combined Joint Task Force - Operation Inherent Resolve (CJTF-OIR), will brief the media live from Baghdad, Iraq on Oct. 21 at 11 a.m. EDT , in the Pentagon Briefing Room
